Invocation Name: everton football club songs
des:
Everton Football Club Songs will bring the sound of Goodison Park right to you. Sing along to Toffee chants and get fired up for game day. This skill will warm the hearts of any Everton fan and teach your friends and family the lyric of the Toffees. Come on Everton!

Is it game day? Ask Alexa to open Everton Football Club Songs and then say, "It's game day!" You will appreciate her response.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
